-- Bharat Forge Looking For Coal Mines in South Africa, Business Line Reports
-- B y   R a k t e e m   K a t a k e y
-- 2010-10-19T01:20:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-19/bharat-forge-looking-for-coal-mines-in-south-africa-business-line-reports.html
Bharat Forge Ltd. is evaluating coal
mines in Mozambique, Indonesia and South Africa that it may
develop for its own captive use, the Business Line newspaper
reported, citing unidentified people.  The company plans to build 10,000 megawatts of power
generating capacity in the 10 years, the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rakteem Katakey in New Delhi at 
 rkatakey@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
